item.title: CVE-2023-28043|2024-08-02T12:30:22.786Z -- dell -- secure%20connect%20gateway
item.description: Dell SCG 5.14 contains an information disclosure vulnerability during the SRS to SCG upgrade path. A remote low privileged malicious user could potentially exploit this vulnerability to retrieve the plain text.
